reviewText: Love this series.  Wish it would come back!
Great series!  too bad it was cancelled.
Very disappointed since I haven't been able to watch it because the dvd cannot be red by the  dvd players actually on sale in London and Europe.
Very good service especially as i live in England,Excellent series look forward to seasons 3 and 4

Just as the season 1 set is great quality, this one is also. In fact the sound is a bit better on this set. Super fast shipping! And I have always loved the show. It shows that the AMERICAN SPIRIT is not dead!
My Mom is going to be so thrilled.  This is her favorite show and she knows all of the family so well.  I got her a calendar last year; can't wait till this comes and I can take it over to her.
